### Library Management System - Users API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api

### ========================================
### CADASTRAR USUÁRIOS
### ========================================

### Cadastrar Estudante
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "city": "São Paulo",
  "category": "STUDENT"
}

